3. Technologies Used

Frontend: HTML5, JavaScript (Fetch API), Bootstrap / Tailwind UI

Backend: Python (FastAPI), httpx, Uvicorn

Data Storage: In-memory (can extend to SQLite / Redis / PostgreSQL)

Deployment: Container-ready (Dockerfile auto-generated)

Cloud Agnostic: Works on AWS, Azure, GCP, or on-prem VMs

